{"tid":797861,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實港大中大兩單殺妻案會唔會都係冤案黎","createTime":"2018-08-29T00:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T00:48:58.000Z","uid":83025,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddbfe223acdeec49fb32d6c9c7cbc5ffaeed84b0","tid":797861,"uid":83025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T00:31:14.000Z","msg":"純粹個人睇法，始終真相唔係由我地去定奪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登咁多位神探可以分享下各自高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中大：<br />\n- 作案工具瑜伽波，點解殺人後唔第一時間拎走要留喺車廂？明明好簡單就可以消滅證據<br />\n- 二女有抑鬱症 (同ADHD?)，大女供詞亦講明由細到大被呀媽管教甚嚴，一直承受巨大壓力，有自殺傾向唔出奇<br />\n- 一氧化碳本來目的可能真係殺鼠用，只係被呀妹拎左去自殺用，攬埋呀媽一齊死<br />\n- 同女學生有長達幾年婚外情，但女學生有明目張膽上門幫姐妹補習，姐係教授屋企一直係知情且勉強接受？唔應該成為殺人嘅導火線<br />\n- 陪審團etc可能係咬住婚外情呢點而有失公正，認為出軌係好大因素導致有動機殺人<br />\n<br />\n港大：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/083045_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F083045_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f1267366&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/083048_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F083048_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=22f531cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/29/083051_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F29%2F083051_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=46a3b98e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(16頁打後)<br />\n港大教授涉嫌殺妻被捕　屍體在疑兇辦公室尋獲<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/zAeAqU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/zAeAqU</a>"},{"pid":"92b484cfa14dcd0a98455e8d9f25f191b0cfdb98","tid":797861,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"